videos.description: Lauri Markkanen goes up top to Wendell Carter Jr. for the jam. John Wall follows it up with a walk-up 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Carter flushes alley-oop dunk, followed by a Wall 3) 2020/12/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Carter flushes alley-oop dunk, followed by a Wall 3

videos.description: DeMarcus Cousins fakes the pass and finds himself open for the three, which he calmly knocks down.

videos.headline: Boogie steps behind the line and drains a 3

videos.description: Coby White makes the pass to Lauri Markkanen who seals his defender for the two-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (White, Markkanen hook up for nice dunk) 2020/12/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: White, Markkanen hook up for nice dunk

videos.description: John Wall shows off his handles and strength as he gets Lauri Markkanen with the hesitation move and finishes the shot plus the contact.

videos.headline: Wall freezes Markkanen with hesitation move, gets and-1

videos.description: Zach LaVine shakes the defender and hits the difficult fadeaway in the corner, on the next possession John Wall backs LaVine down and hits the tough jumper.

videos.headline: LaVine, Wall exchange impressive fadeaways

videos.description: The Bulls get out in transition and it ends with Zach Norvell Jr. making the sweet drop pass to Chandler Hutchison for the dunk.

videos.description: Kenyon Martin Jr., son of the former NBA All-Star, gets a steal and flies down the court for the layup and the foul.
